title: Moonfire 1970 (Action, Adventure) Two truckers! One trip! One triple-cross!

sources.title: Moonfire 1970 (Action, Adventure) Two truckers! One trip! One triple-cross!
sources.description:
A group of truckers find themselves in a dangerous confrontation with a Nazi fugitive hiding in Mexico. Amidst the intense battles and chase scenes, a secondary plot unfolds involving the mysterious disappearance of a reclusive billionaire.

Original title: Moonfire (1970). AKA: Moonfire Trucker 


Director & Writer: Michael Parkhurst
Stars: Richard Egan, Charles Napier, Sonny Liston 
Genres: Action, Adventure, Drama
